---
layout: default

body_classes:
  - wide
---

%h1#photos Photos

- photos_grouped_by_year.each do |(year, year_photos)|
  %h2= year
  %section.photos
    - year_photos.each do |photo|
      .photo
        %a{href: photo.path}
          %img.thumbnail{src: photo.path(rep: :thumbnail), alt: photo[:title], title: photo[:title]}
